@startuml creation-flow
title TripTailor - Itinerary Creation Flow

actor User
participant Frontend
participant "Backend API\n(Spring Boot)" as API
participant "GenAI Service\n(Python)" as AI
participant "Persistence Service\n(Spring Boot)" as PERSIST
database DB

User -> Frontend : Enter trip details
Frontend -> API : POST /trips
API -> AI : POST /schedules
AI -> AI : Call LLM
AI --> API : Return validated schedule
API -> PERSIST : POST /trips?travelerId={id}
PERSIST -> DB : Insert trip, days, activities
DB --> PERSIST : Saved to DB
PERSIST --> API : Saved trip
API --> Frontend : Return itinerary

@enduml
